      <item>
        <title>Create an array containing the alphabet</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;A char list containing the alphabet can be obtained by doing the following:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-elixir&quot; data-lang=&quot;elixir&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sx&quot;&gt;?a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;..&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sx&quot;&gt;?z&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz&#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If desired, we can pass each bitcode to a binary to represent each letter as a
string:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-elixir&quot; data-lang=&quot;elixir&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sx&quot;&gt;?a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;..&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sx&quot;&gt;?z&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;utf8&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;b&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;c&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;d&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;e&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;f&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;g&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;h&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;i&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;j&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;k&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;l&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;m&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;n&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;o&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;p&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;q&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;r&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;s&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;t&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;u&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;v&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;w&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;x&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;y&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;sd&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;z&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional reading:&lt;/strong&gt;
- &lt;a href=&quot;http://elixir-lang.org/getting-started/binaries-strings-and-char-lists.html&quot;&gt;Binaries, strings, and char lists&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
